.TH BUNPY-STDLIB 1 "2026-04-27" "bunpy" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
bunpy-stdlib \- list Python stdlib modules embedded in the binary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bunpy stdlib
[\fImode\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints the Python stdlib modules embedded in this
.B bunpy
binary. The list is generated at build time from the goipy
toolchain's module switch and pinned in
.IR runtime/stdlib_index.go .
CI verifies the file is in sync with the goipy commit on every
push.
.SH MODES
.TP
.B ls
(default) print one module name per line, sorted.
.TP
.B count
print the number of embedded modules.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
print this command's help.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
.RS 4
.nf
$ bunpy stdlib | wc -l
184
$ bunpy stdlib | grep '^math$'
math
$ bunpy stdlib count
184
.fi
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR bunpy (1).
